title: x/mobile: "gomobile bind" errors are not descriptive
body:
`./gomobile bind -target=android TestGoLib`

I never had issues when compiling a single file package, without referencing other packages.

For the first time I tried to add references to structs defined in other packages and I get this error, which I don't understand what it means:
